cause.description:
"Jaluo very complex"-our slogan in the race to make Steven Orengo the new President of the East African republic Kenya.
1. Steven Orengo has to become President for Kenya to make positive progress in the future
2. Only Steven Orengo can liberate us as a country
cause.mission: vote Steven Orengo into the office of the President
cause.name: Steven Orengo for President
